<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yǒu shéi néng yǔ zhǔ jǐng xǐng dào tiān liàng 迦南166</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yǒu shéi néng yǔ zhǔ jǐng xǐng dào tiān liàng
 yǒu shéi néng yǔ zhǔ tóng zǒu zài shí jià lù shàng
 yǒu shéi néng yǔ zhǔ tóng wǎng gè gè tā
 yǒu shéi néng zhēn zhèng tǐ tiē zhǔ xīn cháng
 zhǔ a wǒ yuàn fú zài nǐ ài qí xià
 méi yǒu zì jǐ de xuǎn zé hé mèng xiǎng
 yīn nǐ cí ài de shuāng yǎn shí shí wàng zhe wǒ
 zěn néng zěn néng zài ràng nǐ yōu shāng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>166</hymn_number>
</song>